channel.title: Coords -1, -1? Weird, and really annoying!
channel.description:
I have this huge problem. Sometimes when I log into my server, it teleports me to point -1, -1, resets my account, and leaves me there; and the only way to get out is to use the ::tele command. But, it still resets my account. For me this isn't really a problem, just a minor annoyance, but I can't put my server up 'till I get this fixed, or it may start happening to my players!
Any ideas whats going on?
(P.S. I searched for -1, -1 in my client.java, nothing)
